This paper is about machine learning and its automation, which falls under the category of "cs.LG" (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the shortage of experts in the field of machine learning, which could be categorized under "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence). The proposed approach, RankML, involves predicting the performance of machine learning pipelines, which could be relevant to "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) and "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper discusses the evaluation of the proposed approach, which could be categorized under "cs.SE" (Software Engineering).
